Output docs/screenshots/context-md.png
Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1400
Set Height 900
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set TypingSpeed 50ms

Type "echo '=== Auto-generated by OpenPawl after sprint ===' && echo '' && cat ~/personal/openpawl-test-projects/demo-screenshots/sprint-demo/CONTEXT.md | head -40"
Enter
Sleep 3s
Screenshot docs/screenshots/context-md.png
Sleep 500ms
